definitions.definition: A suburb of Adelaide , South Australia .
A village and civil parish in Westmorland and Furness , Cumbria , England , previously in South Lakeland district ( OS grid ref SD2677 ) .
A suburb of Leigh , Greater Manchester , England ( OS grid ref SJ6599 ) .
A suburb of Lymington in Lymington and Pennington parish, New Forest district, Hampshire , England ( OS grid ref SZ3195 ) .
A coastal town in KwaZulu-Natal , South Africa .
A town in Choctaw County , Alabama .
An unincorporated community in Morgan County , Georgia .
An unincorporated community in Beltrami County , Minnesota , also known as Cass River .
A borough in Mercer County , New Jersey .
An unincorporated community in Houston County and Trinity County , Texas .
An unincorporated community in the town of Prentice , Price County , Wisconsin .
